item.title: Say Hello to Sproutli - World's Largest Vegan & Vegetarian Directory
item.description:
Say Hello to Sproutli - World's Largest Vegan & Vegetarian Directory

Discover vegan-friendly restaurants near you and around the world with Sproutli. With Sproutli, it's never been easier to go vegan and we want to help 1 million people adopt a vegan lifestyle by 2020! Sproutli helps you to find restaurants, cafes, clothing & shoes, accommodation, events, and professionals that are all vegan-friendly.
